# Research Directory

This directory contains codebase research documents created with `/research_codebase`.

## Naming Convention

`YYYY-MM-DD-topic.md`

Example: `2025-01-15-authentication-flow.md`

## Usage

Use `/research_codebase [topic]` to conduct deep codebase investigation.

Research documents include:
- File locations
- Implementation details
- Existing patterns
- External context
